Ahora produciremos un mapa para detectar clÃºsteres y outliers

quadrant <- vector(mode = "numeric", length = nrow(local_univ))

# centers the variable of interest around its mean
m.zc <- ae$ESCOL_PROM - mean(ae$ESCOL_PROM)     

# centers the local Moran's around the mean
m.local <- local_univ[, 1] - mean(local_univ[, 1])    

# significance threshold
signif <- 0.01 

# builds a data quadrant
quadrant[m.zc > 0 & m.local > 0] <- 1  
quadrant[m.zc < 0 & m.local < 0] <- 1      
quadrant[m.zc < 0 & m.local > 0] <- 1
quadrant[m.zc > 0 & m.local < 0] <- 1
quadrant[local_univ[, 5] > signif] <- 0
